description: You scream for ice cream! At least you will when you see Aunt LaLi's fantastic Ice Cream Truck! Serving up your favorite ice cream treats like Haagen Dazs,  Ben & Jerry's, Bomb Pops, Creamsicles, Crunch Bars, Oreos, Minions & Spiderman!  We make hand-crafted Ice Cream Sandwiches, yummy shakes and more! We create hand-crafted sodas and serve organic espresso drinks and iced coffees. Great for events, weddings and festivals.
name: Aunt LaLi's Treats
